data.description: Darling 4 bedroom, 2 bath home located in the established neighborhood of Bellaire Place. Fresh paint throughout and new LVP flooring upstairs and in the downstairs bedroom. Nice open floor-plan with a generous sized family room with a beautiful custom stone, wood-burning fireplace. The kitchen has a large island, granite countertops, gas range, microwave, and dishwasher. Kitchen and eating area have windows overlooking the peaceful backyard. The upstairs bathroom was remodeled in June 2022 and windows replaced in 2014. Good sized lot with beautiful mature trees and a large extended front yard. This home is situated between Dallas and Fort Worth with quick access to 183 and 820.
